---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about this journal and what we write about - web development, JavaScript, modern frameworks, and technology."
>
  <article class="about">
    <header class="about-header">
      <h1>About</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-content">
      <p>
        Welcome. I'm a developer who believes in the power of clear writing and thoughtful
        documentation. This journal is a space to share knowledge, explore ideas, and connect
        with others who care about building things well.
      </p>

      <h2>Topics</h2>
      <p>
        Here you'll find writing on web development, JavaScript and TypeScript, modern frameworks
        and tooling, software design patterns, and occasional explorations of projects and experiments.
      </p>

      <h2>Philosophy</h2>
      <p>
        Good writing clarifies thinking. Whether documenting a technical solution or exploring
        a new concept, the goal is always clarity and usefulness. No fluff, just substance.
      </p>

      <h2>Connect</h2>
      <p>
        Thank you for reading. Feel free to explore the articles and reach out if something resonates.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-header {
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .about-content {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-content p {
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .about-content h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
</style>
